data.description: Under Construction. Under construction to be built, LGI Homes is proud to present the Sorrento, a move-in ready home with three bedrooms, two-and-a-half bathrooms and an open-concept floor plan. Located near Wesley Chapel, this brand-new dream home is only minutes away from the life of the city. A highlight of the home is the chef-ready kitchen with stainless-steel appliances, quartz countertops and tall wood cabinets. Any and all who step in will spot eye-catching details and upgraded finishes upon entering the home. Two stories make for even more space in this unique floor plan. A full bath and separate utility room on the second floor make for even more convenience to families living in the Sorrento. The master bathroom includes a double-sink vanity, shower & tub, and an extra door for additional privacy.
